snippet.title: Mekkablood: Quarry Assault Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3056270/Mekkablood_Quarry_Assault/
KRUMB Games discord server! https://discord.gg/u8wF5J92Y2
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/KRUMBGames

Special thanks to Geoff Galneda for doing the voicework.

Mekkablood: Quarry Assault is a fast paced Boomer Shooter / Retro FPS that you play while piloting a mech! #trailertuesday 

Music created with Suno
